'''西印度聖螺'''（學名：''{{lang|la|Turbinella angulata}}''），又名'''西印度鉛螺'''或'''燈螺'''，是[[熱帶|熱帶]]海域一種非常大的[[海螺|海螺]]，有[[鰓|鰓]]和[[螺厣|螺厣]]，是[[拳螺科|拳螺科]][[鉛螺屬|鉛螺屬]]之下的一個[[腹足綱|腹足綱]][[軟體動物|軟體動物]]的[[物種|物種]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.biolib.cz/en/taxon/id575885/ |title=Biolib |access-date=2018-05-11 |archive-date=2019-09-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190922132315/https://www.biolib.cz/en/taxon/id575885/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

The name "chank" for the shell of this species is derived from the word [[shankha|shankha]], the divine conch or sacred conch, ''[[Turbinella_pyrum|Turbinella pyrum]]'', a closely related species from the [[Indian_Ocean|Indian Ocean]].<ref name=EE>{{Cite web |url=http://www.backyardnature.net/mexnat/chank.htm |title=Backyard Nature |access-date=2018-05-11 |archive-date=2020-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200616022549/https://www.backyardnature.net/mexnat/chank.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==分佈==
西印度聖螺分佈在[[西大西洋|西大西洋]]，由[[佛羅里達礁島群|佛羅里達礁島群]]及[[巴哈馬|巴哈馬]]南至[[古巴|古巴]]、[[多明尼加共和國|多明尼加共和國]]、[[牙買加|牙買加]]及[[海地|海地]]，並[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]、[[伯利茲|伯利茲]]、[[洪都拉斯|洪都拉斯]]、[[尼加拉瓜|尼加拉瓜]]、[[哥斯達黎加|哥斯達黎加]]、[[巴拿馬|巴拿馬]]及[[哥倫比亞|哥倫比亞]]的[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]海岸{{r|Malacolog|WoRMS_420076}}<ref name=AA>{{Cite web |url=http://www.malacolog.org/search.php?nameid=5500 |title=Malacog - A Database of Western Atlantic Marine Mollusca |access-date=2010-06-25 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303231316/http://www.malacolog.org/search.php?nameid=5500 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>Claudio Galli: [http://www.bagniliggia.it/WMSD/SearchSpecies.php?freeText=&inputFamily=&inputGenus=turbinella&inputSpecies=angulata&inputVariety=&inputAuthor=&B1=Search  WMSDB - Wolrdwide Mollusc Species Data Base]</ref><ref name=DD>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gastropods.com/2/Shell_1512.shtml |title=Hardy's Internet Guide to Marine Gastropods |access-date=2018-05-11 |archive-date=2020-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812111125/http://www.gastropods.com/2/Shell_1512.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>
